<args_desc>
- `-copy`: Copies a file or a folder.
</args_desc>
<md>
#### Copying (`-copy`)
Copies a file or folder to a new location.

**Syntax:** `MANAGE -copy [-dir] <source> to <destination>`

```
<-@ Copy the configuration file to backup @->
<@|MANAGE -copy @ROOT/config.ini to @ROOT/config.bak
---end---
```

</md>